{"word":"G3340 - μετανοέω - metanoéō - met-an-o-eh'-o - Repent","slug":"G3340","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετανοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>metanoéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>met-an-o-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Repent"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - metanoeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>met-an-o-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G3539\">G3539</a>; to <i>think differently</i> or <i>afterwards</i>, that is, <i>reconsider</i> (morally to <i>feel compunction</i>): - repent."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2132\">G2132</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3539\">G3539</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5282\">G5282</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283\">G5283</a>"}]}